{"tid":2198954,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"夕爺寫既忘記有時歌詞真係好撚正","createTime":"2020-09-11T18:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T19:49:04.000Z","uid":212249,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"72884d52d1134c465b95eaf6db2288baf4a898f2","tid":2198954,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T18:42:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JpZxhuklvmk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJpZxhuklvmk&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fle0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=19dddc88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JpZxhuklvmk</a><br />\n<br />\n作曲 王菀之<br />\n填詞 林夕<br />\n編曲/監製 馮翰銘<br />\n<br />\n有時無心的散聚<br />\n後來讓誰住心裏<br />\n那時聊天不覺累<br />\n但回味過更空虛<br />\n<br />\n客途來又去的客人<br />\n誰又似至親 真的肯等<br />\n<br />\n難得相逢時 回頭生疏至此<br />\n如今失眠時 誰還很想要知<br />\n誰在最後及時相知一輩子<br />\n誰在記憶只剩名字想念面容與 誰相似<br />\n誰生不逢時 提前穿好戒指<br />\n誰姍姍來遲 仍能與我分享往事 添一雙筷子<br />\n<br />\n每場人生的宴會<br />\n面容淡忘在椅背<br />\n有時隨便講再會<br />\n後來或懊悔 有幾多個<br />\n真可再乾杯<br />\n<br />\n曾經相逢時 回頭生疏至此<br />\n如今失眠時 誰還很想要知<br />\n誰在最後及時相知一輩子<br />\n誰在記憶只剩名字想念面容與 誰相似<br />\n情生不逢時 才忘記那陣時<br />\n誰姍姍來遲 才能夠記得一輩子<br />\n應該想起的 想一次<br />\n不必掛心的 即管試一試<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12db48f5a3449d7785737ad2b4f2472070b58ce5","tid":2198954,"uid":166400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T19:31:37.000Z","msg":"夕爺真係好撚正"},{"pid":"147c4c8656c3268872a684ee1364c0a7a1a904d6","tid":2198954,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T19:45:10.000Z","msg":"難得相逢時 回頭生疏至此<br />\n如今失眠時 誰還很想要知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36134b1c28c2c76b17a6d6edc06205c1ac55c8f2","tid":2198954,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T19:47:03.000Z","msg":"首歌係幾好聽"},{"pid":"957ad102db3c9e6b213d1293a2b45f6c42584397","tid":2198954,"uid":199633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T19:49:04.000Z","msg":"Ivana都係滄海遺珠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}